posts.name: Sean Ernstes
posts.cooked:
Hi! There is a known issue where a race condition in the Quest-side network tables implementation causes the first request sent to be discarded. This is fixed in an upcoming release of QuestNav (hopefully sometime within the next two weeks). The easiest workaround right now is to call the reset pose method twice.

Hope this helps! Ping me again if you need more help

posts.name: Sean Ernstes
posts.cooked:
Also, you may get quicker support if you join the QuestNav discord

A place to discuss and get help using QuestNav on your FRC robot | 122 members
